      "id": "p004",
      "index": 4,
      "source": "Each LPX compute tray or node has 16 LPUs with 2 Altera FPGAs, 1 Intel Granite Rapids host CPU and 1 BlueField-4 front-end module. As with other Nvidia systems, hyperscalers customers can and will use their own Front-end NIC of choice rather than paying for Nvidia’s BlueField.",
